gantt
    title Hadith Analysis Platform — Implementation Timeline
    dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat %b %d

    section Phase 0: Scaffold
    Repo structure & Pydantic models    :done, p0a, 2026-03-20, 3d
    Docker compose (Neo4j + PG)         :done, p0b, after p0a, 2d
    Makefile & CI skeleton              :done, p0c, after p0b, 2d

    section Phase 1: Acquire & Parse
    Data downloaders (7 sources)        :done, p1a, after p0c, 5d
    LK + Sanadset parsers              :done, p1b, after p1a, 4d
    Thaqalayn + Sunnah parsers         :done, p1c, after p1a, 4d
    Arabic text utilities              :done, p1d, after p1a, 3d
    Supplementary parsers + tests      :done, p1e, after p1b, 3d

    section Phase 2: Entity Resolution
    Rule-based narrator NER            :done, p2a, after p1e, 5d
    Narrator disambiguation pipeline   :done, p2b, after p2a, 10d
    Hadith dedup (embeddings + FAISS)  :done, p2c, after p2a, 7d
    Human-in-the-loop review           :done, p2d, after p2b, 5d

    section Phase 3: Graph Construction
    Node loading (Neo4j batch)         :done, p3a, after p2d, 4d
    Edge loading (chains + parallels)  :done, p3b, after p3a, 5d
    Validation queries                 :done, p3c, after p3b, 3d

    section Phase 4: Enrichment
    Graph metrics (centrality, etc.)   :done, p4a, after p3c, 5d
    Topic classification (zero-shot)   :done, p4b, after p3c, 5d
    Historical overlay curation        :done, p4c, after p3c, 7d
    Analytical query library           :done, p4d, after p4a, 5d

    section Phase 5: Interface
    FastAPI backend                    :done, p5a, after p4d, 7d
    Graph visualization (D3/vis.js)    :done, p5b, after p5a, 7d
    Search + comparative views         :done, p5c, after p5b, 7d

    section Phase 6: Testing & Quality
    Testcontainers + real data flow    :done, p6a, after p5c, 5d
    Negative/fuzz testing              :done, p6b, after p6a, 4d
    Coverage push to 90%               :done, p6c, after p6a, 5d
    Browser automation (Playwright)    :done, p6d, after p6b, 3d

    section Phase 7: Security & Ops
    Data retooling + tech debt         :done, p7a, after p6c, 5d
    OAuth auth + JWT + 2FA design      :done, p7b, after p7a, 5d
    OWASP hardening + CI security      :done, p7c, after p7b, 3d
    Docs, diagrams, CI optimization    :active, p7d, after p7c, 3d
